snippet.title: Somnium Trailer
snippet.description:
Your email has been lost in transit! You must navigate this colorful and strange landscape and recover it before it is lost!

A project by Evan Nave and Luke Mirman.

Play the game at: https://lmirman.itch.io/somnium
